---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
import '../styles/globals.css';
import { FiShield } from 'react-icons/fi';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Mentis Aura"
  description="Privacy policy for Mentis Aura. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <Navigation client:load />

  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
        <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, white 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 30px 30px;"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-green-600 rounded-2xl mb-8 shadow-xl">
          <FiShield className="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 font-playfair">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-200">Last Updated: January 2025</p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">We collect minimal data. We never sell your information.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-playfair prose-headings:text-gray-900 prose-h2:text-3xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-6 prose-h3:text-xl prose-h3:mt-8 prose-h3:mb-4 prose-a:text-blue-600 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline">

        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          Mentis Aura LLC ("we," "us," "our") operates mentisaura.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you purchase books or interact with our website.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect minimal data necessary for order fulfillment:</p>

        <h3>Order Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and shipping address (for physical books)</li>
          <li>Email address (for order confirmation and ebook delivery)</li>
          <li>Order details (products purchased, format, quantity)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Payment Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>We do NOT collect or store payment card information</li>
          <li>All payment processing is handled by Stripe, Inc.</li>
          <li>Your payment data never touches our servers</li>
          <li>See Stripe's Privacy Policy at <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stripe.com/privacy</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Technical Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Basic analytics (pages visited, device type, location by country)</li>
          <li>Cookies for essential website functionality</li>
          <li>IP address for fraud prevention</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

        <h3>Order Fulfillment</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Processing and shipping your order</li>
          <li>Sending order confirmations and tracking information</li>
          <li>Delivering ebooks via email</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Communication</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Responding to inquiries and support requests</li>
          <li>Sending transactional emails about your order</li>
          <li>Newsletter updates (only if you explicitly subscribe)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Business Operations</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Improving website functionality</li>
          <li>Preventing fraud</li>
          <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>We Never</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Sell your data to third parties</li>
          <li>Use your data for advertising</li>
          <li>Share your information except with service providers necessary for order fulfillment</li>
          <li>Send unsolicited marketing emails</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use these services to operate our business:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Stripe:</strong> Payment processing (see <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stripe.com/privacy</a>)</li>
          <li><strong>Lulu xPress:</strong> Print-on-demand production and shipping</li>
          <li><strong>Email Provider:</strong> Order confirmations and ebook delivery</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymous website usage data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Each service has its own privacy policy. We choose providers with strong privacy practices.</p>

        <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Your data is stored securely using industry-standard encryption</li>
          <li>Physical book orders: Data retained for 7 years (tax/legal requirements)</li>
          <li>Ebook orders: Email address retained unless you request deletion</li>
          <li>Payment data: Never stored on our servers (Stripe only)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your data (subject to legal retention requirements)</li>
          <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request your data in a portable format</li>
          <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise these rights, contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@mentisaura.com">privacy@mentisaura.com</a></p>

        <h2>GDPR Compliance (EU Customers)</h2>
        <p>For EU residents:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Legal basis for processing: Contract fulfillment and legitimate business interests</li>
          <li>Data transferred to US (Stripe, Lulu) under appropriate safeguards</li>
          <li>Right to lodge complaint with your supervisory authority</li>
          <li>Data retention: As specified above</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our website is not directed to individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use minimal cookies for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Essential website functionality (shopping cart, security)</li>
          <li>Basic analytics (anonymous, no cross-site tracking)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note: Disabling essential cookies may prevent you from placing orders.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy. Changes effective when posted. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Privacy questions: <a href="mailto:privacy@mentisaura.com">privacy@mentisaura.com</a></p>
        <p>General inquiries: <a href="mailto:contact@mentisaura.com">contact@mentisaura.com</a></p>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 mt-8">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Mentis Aura LLC</p>
          <p>30 N Gould St Ste R<br/>Sheridan, WY 82801<br/>United States</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer client:load />
</Layout>
